<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="two-col">
      <div class="body-text">
        <p class="sl">Airbnb & Short-Term Rental Service</p>
        <h2>A 1-star review about a broken refrigerator is preventable</h2>
        <p>Airbnb hosts in LA manage a specific kind of appliance stress. Guests use appliances harder and less carefully than long-term tenants. The refrigerator in a WeHo short-term rental gets packed and unpacked every few days. The washing machine in a Silver Lake Airbnb runs a full load within hours of every check-in. These aren't complaints — it's just what short-term rental use looks like.</p>
        <p>When something breaks, the window to fix it is tight. You've got a check-out at 11am and a check-in at 3pm. If the refrigerator stopped cooling overnight and you find out at 10am, you have a four-hour window to get it fixed before your next guests arrive. That's an Airbnb problem we solve constantly for hosts across LA.</p>
        <p>Most of our Airbnb clients manage their properties remotely. They're not present during service. Lockbox codes, key fob instructions, building entry procedures — we handle all of it. You provide access when you book, we handle the rest, and we send you a completion confirmation so you can update your listing status and message your incoming guests that everything is ready.</p>
        <p>LA buildings with short-term rentals often have rules about service vendors — specifically, they require a certificate of insurance naming the building manager as additional insured. We carry this and have it ready before we walk in the door. No friction with your building management over vendor insurance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-box">
        <h3>Airbnb Service Line</h3>
        <p>Appliance broken between guest stays? Call now.</p>
        <a href="tel:+14243250520" class="cta-phone">☎ (424) 325-0520</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="cta-book">Request Service Online</a>
        <p class="cta-note">Licensed · COI Available · Remote Host Friendly</p>
        <div class="price-mini">
          <div class="pm-row"><span class="pm-label">Diagnostic fee</span><span class="pm-val">$89</span></div>
          <div class="pm-row"><span class="pm-label">Applied to repair</span><span class="pm-val">Yes</span></div>
          <div class="pm-row"><span class="pm-label">Lockbox / key fob access</span><span class="pm-val">Yes</span></div>
          <div class="pm-row"><span class="pm-label">COI on request</span><span class="pm-val">Available</span></div>
          <div class="pm-row"><span class="pm-label">Completion confirmation</span><span class="pm-val">Included</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

