        <div class="fact">
          <h4>🏠 WeHo & Silver Lake — top LA Airbnb markets</h4>
          <p>Among the highest short-term rental density in LA County. Compact apartments, stacked laundry, high turnover. Appliance failures happen fast and need fast fixes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fact">
          <h4>⭐ 1-star reviews are preventable</h4>
          <p>"The refrigerator didn't work" and "the washer broke" are the most common appliance-related Airbnb complaints. Same-day repair between stays prevents them.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fact">
          <h4>📋 Building COI requirements</h4>
          <p>LA condo buildings and HOAs increasingly require COI from all service vendors. We have it ready — no delays because of building management insurance requirements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fact">
          <h4>🌊 Venice & Santa Monica — coastal effects</h4>
          <p>Airbnbs near the beach face accelerated coil corrosion from salt air. Refrigerator and A/C coil cleaning intervals are shorter than inland properties.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

